{"version":1,"entries":{"person_78878_translations":{"at":1772647160264,"data":{"id":78878,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Xing Yu gained his fame after playing the role of Coolie in the movie Kung Fu Hustle. He was a 32nd generation martial monk at Shaolin Temple on Mount Song. He has practiced martial art under the direction of Master De Yang at the temple for 10 years since age 12. He currently takes part in multiple movie projects in Asia, including Flash Point and Ip Man with Donnie Yen and director Wilson Yip.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Xing Yu, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Xing Yu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"석행우","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　释彦能（释行宇）是河南嵩山少林寺第32代弟子，12岁皈依少林，拜少林寺武僧队总教头德扬禅师习武参禅，历时十一年。曾代表少林寺武僧队出访欧美、东南亚等数十国家进行功夫表演及友好访问。2003年在偶然机会下为周星驰所赏识，初登大银幕，参与拍摄电影《功夫》，担演其中主要角色“十二路谭腿”苦力强。后在甄子丹主演的《叶问》中出演武痴林，最近在刘德华和谢霆锋主演的《新少林寺》中饰演少林武僧净空，有出色表现。","name":"Xing Yu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"释行宇（释彦能），1978年12月27日出生于山东省济南市章丘区，中国功夫演员。河南嵩山少林寺第32代弟子，12岁皈依少林，拜少林寺武僧队总教头德扬禅师习武参禅，历时十一年。曾代表少林寺武僧队出访欧美、东南亚等数十国家进行功夫表演及友好访问。2003年在偶然机会下为周星驰所赏识，初登大银幕，参与拍摄电影《功夫》，担演其中主要角色“十二路谭腿”苦力强。后在甄子丹主演的《叶问》中出演武痴林，最近在刘德华和谢霆锋主演的《新少林寺》中饰演少林武僧净空，有出色表现。","name":"释行宇","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Thích Ngạn Năng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"釋彥能（釋行宇）是河南嵩山少林寺第 32 代弟子，12 歲皈依少林，拜少林寺武僧隊總教頭德揚禪師習武參禪，歷時十一年。曾代表少林寺武僧隊出訪歐美、東南亞等數十國家進行功夫表演及友好訪問。2003 年在偶然機會下為周星馳所賞識，初登大銀幕，參與拍攝電影《功夫》，擔演其中主要角色“十二路譚腿”苦力強。後在甄子丹主演的《葉問》中出演武痴林，最近在劉德華和謝霆鋒主演的《新少林寺》中飾演少林武僧淨空，有出色表現。","name":"釋行宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Син Юй","primary":false}}]}},"person_1245099_translations":{"at":1772647173453,"data":{"id":1245099,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Huh Yi-jae is a South Korean actress.","name":"Huh Yi-jae","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"허이재","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韩国演员","name":"申在伊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"許怡才","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國演員","name":"許怡才","primary":false}}]}},"person_2020073_translations":{"at":1772647179172,"data":{"id":2020073,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Chikahiro Kobayashi (小林 親弘, Kobayashi Chikahiro, September 5, 1983) is a Japanese actor and voice actor born in Aichi Prefecture, currently affiliated with Enkikaku.","name":"Chikahiro Kobayashi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小林亲弘是日本男性演员和声优。出生于日本爱知县。","name":"小林亲弘","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小林親弘是日本的男性聲優、演員。出身於愛知縣，畢業於圓演劇研究所，所屬公司為 Atomic Monkey。","name":"小林親弘","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"小林親弘","primary":true}},{"iso_31